Violet Mersereau https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Violet_Mersereau 0 Violet Mersereau (October 2, 1892 – November 12, 1975) was an American stage and film actress. Over the course of her screen career, Mersereau appeared in over 100 short and silent film features.
